This will wake you up before you go-go – Club Tropicana is more than just a song by Wham! It’s also an easy, alcohol-free party drink that’ll keep you limbo-dancing all day and all night. Serves 1 230g tinned pineapple, drained 100g natural yoghurt50ml coconut water5g ginger root100g fresh mango flesh20ml runny honey20ml lemon1 tinned pineapple ring, to garnish Blend all the ingredients bar the garnish with four ice cubes for 30 seconds, then pour into a suitable glass. Hang the pineapple ring on the rim and serve. Umbrella and straw optional, but recommended. • JJ Goodman, London Cocktail Club. The book, Kitchen Cocktails by JJ Goodman, is out now.